<DOCNO> NYT20000801.0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-01 11:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9288 &Cx1f; tad-z
r l BC-MONEYTALK0802-COX     08-01 1067
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MONEYTALK0802-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Social Security site offers a way to figure benefits
 &HT;    By Hank Ezell
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
