can be used at the Sydney Games. The panel reviewed a combined
blood-urine test for EPO that was developed by Australian and
French teams. The testing now must be considered by the IOC's
lawyers. Final approval would come at the IOC executive board
meeting in Lausanne on Aug. 28-29. (Summary from wires) By Jere
Longman.
