just don't cut it anymore with the well-heeled set. AmEx has
launched its BlackCard of Centurion Card which comes with an annual
fee of $1,000 and MBNA has launched the Quantum Card with a credit
line of $1 million. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH GRAPHIC.
