delegate from Lufkin, Texas, the Republican Party's ``determination
to restore integrity, truthfulness and decency to the presidency
overshadows all the other issues,'' including abortion rights and
gun control. ``Personally,'' he said, ``I don't think there's a
more important issue than the issue of life, but those of us who
disagree aren't being combative or angry about it.'' (Murray, Cox
News Service)
