   ELECTRICPOWER-SOUTH _ The FPL-Entergy marriage looks to put the
new utility in the catbird seat when it comes to electric power in
the South and future deregulation. We'll take a look at the
ramifications of the combination for energy needs, business
competition, etc. We'll also ask if the move will affect plans by
companies such as Duke Power to put
</P>
<P>
   wholesale power plants in Fla. (Circelli, Palm Beach Post).
