just don't cut it anymore with the well-heeled set. AmEx has
launched its BlackCard of Centurion Card which comes with an annual
fee of $1,000 and MBNA has launched the Quantum Card with a credit
line of $1 million. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   MONEYTALK _ Now, any worker over age 25 can go to the Social
Security Administration's Web site _ www.ssa.gov/retire _ and
figure out the retirement benefit he or she can expect. (Ezell,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED.
