boring. Nintendo is just about the only one to make a decent stab
at tennis, and you probably don't even remember it: ``Mario's 3D
Tennis'' for the company's now-defunct Virtual Boy system. The
three of you who bought it know what I'm talking about. By MALCOLM
MAYHEW. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
