<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-01 20:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9816 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2N     08-01 0681
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2NDLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Tuesday, Aug. 1, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
