<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-01 20:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9884 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r f BC-LLOYD-COLUMN-LADN     08-01 0782
