</P>
<P>
   Volkswagen's sales climbed 4.8 percent, while Toyota's sales
crept up 1 percent and Nissan's sales edged up by 0.2 percent.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-08-01-00 2136EDT &QL; 
