   &QL; 
 &UR; GROW (`GROW A BUSINESS' COLUMN) _  &LR; Setting up online marketplaces
can be quite risky, as stories and stock prices have recently
shown. But that hasn't deterred two San Francisco attorneys from
separately giving up the practice of law to practice
entrepreneurship.
</P>
<P>
   One of them is Dmitry Shubov, who tapped the computer
programming talents of fellow Russian-Jewish immigrants to create
LegalMatch, a Web site to connect lawyers with consumers.  &UR; COLUMN &LR; 
 &UR; BY PETER SINTON &LR;
