<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-01 23:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0160 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-NY-MRS-CLINTON-NYT     08-01 0506
